.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Movie-Genre: epic, martial-arts, scientific, zombie
Nationality: australian, british, colombian, french
1. Nationality:colombian is on the right of Movie-Genre:zombie##1
2. Nationality:colombian is between Nationality:british and Movie-Genre:martial-arts##2
3. Nationality:british is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:french is on the left of Movie-Genre:scientific##1
5. Movie-Genre:martial-arts == Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | zombie    | epic | martial-arts   | scientific  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

